OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FThe King has acknowledged victims of
OL,7,Fsexual abuse in the wake of the
OL,8,FJeffrey Epstein scandal highlighting
OL,9,Fin a speech to Congress the
OL,10,F"collective strength" of the UK and US
OL,11,Fto support survivors.
OL,13,FCharles delivered an address to both
OL,14,Fhouses on Capitol Hill telling the
OL,15,Fassembled politicians the partnership
OL,16,Fbetween the two nations is "more
OL,17,Fimportant today than it has ever been".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@UO]xD@\OUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
