OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FAnd he said when Britain and America
OL,7,Fdrew on their common values to come
OL,8,Ftogether: "This, I believe, is the
OL,9,Fspecial ingredient in our
OL,10,Frelationship".
OL,12,FThe head of state touched on topics
OL,13,Fsuch as support for Ukraine and the
OL,14,F"collapse of critical natural systems"
OL,15,F` issues not in favour with President
OL,16,FDonald Trump ` and said the essence of
OL,17,FBritain and America was a "duty to
OL,18,Ffoster compassion, to promote peace"
OL,19,Fand "value all people, of all faiths,
OL,20,Fand of none".
