OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FThe attempted assassination of the
OL,7,Fpresident at a Washington media dinner
OL,8,Fon Saturday evening was condemned by
OL,9,Fthe King, who said "such acts of
OL,10,Fviolence will never succeed".
OL,12,FDuring his speech in the Hall of the
OL,13,FHouse, whose public and press
OL,14,Fgalleries were packed, the King spoke
OL,15,Fof the importance of Nato, the value
OL,16,Fof European partners and the need to
OL,17,Freduce world conflicts, stemming the
OL,18,F"beating of ploughshares into swords",
OL,19,Fall priorities for Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,20,FGovernment.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@\O]zD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
