OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FWith the Queen sitting nearby the King
OL,7,Fsaid: "Distinguished members of the
OL,8,F119th Congress, it is here in these
OL,9,Fvery halls that this spirit of liberty
OL,10,Fand the promise of America's Founders
OL,11,Fis present in every session and every
OL,12,Fvote cast.
OL,14,F"Not by the will of one, but by the
OL,15,Fdeliberation of many, representing the
OL,16,Fliving mosaic of the United States.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777420987
OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,F"In both of our countries, it is the
OL,7,Fvery fact of our vibrant, diverse and
OL,8,Ffree societies that gives us our
OL,9,Fcollective strength, including to
OL,10,Fsupport victims of some of the ills
OL,11,Fthat, so tragically, exist in both our
OL,12,Fsocieties today."
OL,14,FThere have been repeated calls by the
OL,15,Ffamily of Virginia Giuffre, a victim
OL,16,Fof convicted paedophile Jeffrey
OL,17,FEpstein, for a meeting with the King
OL,18,Fand Queen, but sources have previously
OL,19,Fsaid the couple will not meet them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
