OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FThe legal implications of Charles and
OL,7,FCamilla coming into contact with any
OL,8,Fsurvivors of paedophile financier
OL,9,FEpstein, and the King's constitutional
OL,10,Fposition, make a meeting impossible
OL,11,Fwhile there are ongoing UK police
OL,12,Finvestigations into matters related to
OL,13,FEpstein.
OL,15,FCharles is midway through a four-day
OL,16,Fstate visit to mark the 250th
OL,17,Fanniversary of American independence
OL,18,Fand he spoke about bonds between
OL,19,Fformer enemies, the US and Britain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
