OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,F"The Alliance that our two Nations
OL,7,Fhave built over the centuries ` and
OL,8,Ffor which we are profoundly grateful
OL,9,Fto the American people ` is truly
OL,10,Funique," said the King.
OL,12,FAddressing Mike Johnson, speaker of
OL,13,Fthe House of Representatives, He went
OL,14,Fon to say: "That partnership, I
OL,15,Fbelieve Mr Speaker, is more important
OL,16,Ftoday than it has ever been."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]vD@LOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
