OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FGuest speakers on Capitol Hill
OL,7,Ftraditional receive brief standing
OL,8,Fovations on points that resonate with
OL,9,Fpoliticians and the King was afforded
OL,10,Fthat honour when he mentioned the gun
OL,11,Fattack against the president.
OL,13,FHe said: "We meet, too, in the
OL,14,Faftermath of the incident not far from
OL,15,Fthis great building that sought to
OL,16,Fharm the leadership of your nation and
OL,17,Fto foment wider fear and discord.
OL,19,F"Let me say with unshakeable resolve:
OL,20,Fsuch acts of violence will never
OL,21,Fsucceed.
OL,26,@uD@JOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
