OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FAnd notably, when the monarch called
OL,7,Ffor the same "unyielding resolve" to
OL,8,Fbe shown for Ukraine as that in the
OL,9,Fwake of the 9/11 attacks a number of
OL,10,Fmembers on the Republican side of the
OL,11,Fchamber did not rise to their feet
OL,12,Fwith others and clap.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@aO]
