OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FA Buckingham Palace spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"The King was deeply honoured to have
OL,8,Fbeen invited to be the first British
OL,9,Fking to give such an address and was
OL,10,Fgreatly touched by the warmth and
OL,11,Fgenerosity of the response he
OL,12,Freceived."
OL,14,FEarlier the King and president sat
OL,15,Fdown for bilateral talks in the White
OL,16,FHouse's famous Oval Office where the
OL,17,Fdeveloping relationship was revealed
OL,18,Fby Mr Trump touching the King's knee.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
