OL,3,CKing hails 'truly unique' alliance in
OL,4,Cspeech to US Congress
OL,6,FFormer first lady Michelle Obama
OL,7,Ffamously put her hand around Queen
OL,8,FElizabeth II during a G20 reception in
OL,9,F2009 and the monarch returned the
OL,10,Fgesture.
OL,12,FAfter the bilateral when questioned by
OL,13,Fpress as he left, Mr Trump said: "It
OL,14,Fwas a really good meeting.
OL,16,F"He's a fantastic person. They're
OL,17,Fincredible people and it's a real
OL,18,Fhonour."
OL,26,@uD@bOUxD@AOUzD@HO]
